         MACRO
         SENSEG &NAME,&PARENT=$$$$$$$$,&LEVEL=0
         DS    0D                  ALIGNMENT
         DC    CL8'&NAME'          NAME OF SEGMENT
         DC    CL8'&PARENT'        NAME OF PARENT
         DC    F'&LEVEL'           LEVEL OF THIS SEGMENT
         DC    F'0'                WORK AREA FOR SEGMENT
         MEND
